div.head: Description of changes for 2012.11
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft copied ffrom a descriptive transcription of the St. Victor manuscript. Corrections and additions await a collation comparision of available manuscript witnesses. A transcription of the Sorbonne manuscript still needs to be completed. Citations, cross-references, and a critical apparatus also still await construction.
